state_description: This screen indicates that the cleanup process is complete. It shows the amount of space cleaned and provides options to share the results or explore additional cleanup options.

enables.name: Share Results
enables.description: Allows the user to share the cleanup results.

enables.name: Try Get Rid of Duplicate Files
enables.description: Prompts the user to try removing duplicate files using Gemini to free up more space.

enables.name: View Log
enables.description: Allows the user to view the log of the cleanup process.

enables.name: Start Over
enables.description: Allows the user to restart the cleanup process.
